* **\#2 Ghost\_English\_Lyrics:** *In the space of time / I found a line / A string of time / A line divine / A line of rhyme / The time divined / The timing / Of rhyming / The time, to find / A line, a sign / We wait for time / To find its rhyme / Your string in mine / I found a line / A string of time / A line in rhyme*

